gameoflife

Class Cell

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameoflife.Cell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Cell>

    public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Cell>
    The class represents a cell in the Game Of Life, needed for the boundless representation of the field.

    Besides two basic constructors, it also overrides the Object.equals and Object.toString methods. The class also implements the Comparable interface for testing purposes.
